---
description: React conventions
globs:
  - "client/**/*.jsx"
alwaysApply: false
---
- Functional components + hooks only.
- Role-based UI: don't just hide buttons for unauthorized roles — the
  backend must also reject the action. UI hiding is convenience, not security.
- Forms touching money (maintenance payment, expense entry) must show a
  confirmation step before submit.
- Keep API calls in a dedicated client/src/api/ layer, not inline in components.